data.description: You're coming home to Jonathan Ct! This charming and bright home is conveniently located on a peaceful cul-de-sac in Oldham County with easy access to       I-265 & I-71. It features NEW FLOORS, new paint, an open floor plan and the 1st floor also includes a large family room with a fireplace and vaulted ceiling. The kitchen has stainless appliances, a gas range, and beautiful back splash. The 2nd floor features a large loft, three large bedrooms and a full Jack and Jill bath. Relax on the cozy covered front porch or on the private back patio. The large backyard is fully fenced. The 2 1/2 car garage includes plenty of room for storage. Come take a look today!
